	    -  tlemea_entities.xml reference file name changed to gale_entities.xml
	    - %galenet.entites changed to gale.entities

	    - Modified the structure of x-y coordinate pairs with comma separators

	    - Element CLEMEANP modified as GALENP
	    - Comment included for the Copyright element
	    - format of da and tdate elements (dd/mm/yy) changed to dd/mm/yyyy
	    - Removed JournalTitle, navi, navp, imagecount and table elements									

28/07/09  1.2	HTC	Original version  - tdate element format changed from dd/mm/yyyy to yyyymmdd

31/07/09  1.3	HTC  Comment modified for the Copyright element based on confirmation
   
14/09/09  1.4	HTC	Original version  - da element format changed from dd/mm/yyyy to month dd, yyyy

18/09/09  1.5  HTC  Original version  - supptitle and suppsubtitle removed at issue level and included at article level
									    			    - Image file naming convensions changed to pubcode-yyyy-mmdd-pppp

25/09/09  1.6  HTC  Original version  - DTD name changed from GALENP.dtd to FT.dtd
